<section id="empGroup">
  <title><indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>employees</primary>
      <secondary>creating new groups for</secondary>
    </indexterm>New Employee Group</title>
  <para>To create a new Employee Group, use the following screen:</para>
  <para><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/empGroup.png" />
        </imageobject>
        <caption>Create New Employee Group</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot></para>
  <para>When creating a new Employee Group, you are presented with the
  following options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Name</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Enter a name to identify the Employee Group.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Description</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Enter a brief description of the Employee Group.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Member Employees</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Displays information about any Employees who have been added to
        the Employee Group.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>
